steps.description:
The pistol is great, because it takes only five shots to the body or three to the head to kill someone. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ca/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/ca/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet1.jpg/aid155447-v4-728px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":288,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"455","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

The sniper rifle is also one of the best, as it takes about two shots to the body to kill, or one shot to the head. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/1b/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/1/1b/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet2.jpg/aid155447-v4-728px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":288,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"455","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Explosive weapons like the rocket launcher and fuel gun are only good for vehicles and suicide kills. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/70/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/7/70/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet3.jpg/aid155447-v4-728px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":288,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"455","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

All other weapons should only be used if you're really bored and don't care about dying, including vehicles. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b6/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/b/b6/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet4.jpg/aid155447-v4-728px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":288,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"455","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Tanks may rally you a couple of spawn kills, but as soon as someone throws a grenade at you, which is easy, you're dead. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/3d/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet5.jpg/v4-460px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet5.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/3/3d/Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet5.jpg/aid155447-v4-728px-Play-Halo-Well-Step-13Bullet5.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":288,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"455","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
